A collection of basic C libraries I implemented during my Summer break in 2024.
While taking COMP20003 (Algorithms and Data Structures), I implemented some more interesting structures.

Source for each library is in a folder starting with "Lib". The rest are example programs that can be compiled using the Makefile.

""

Implemented so far:

Abstract Data Structures:
- Linked Lists + Stacks + Queues
- Hash Table with Separate Chaining

Graph Data Structure:
- Binary Search Trees
- PATRICIA Trie 

Probabilistic: 
- Skip Lists
- Bloom Filter
- Cuckoo Filter